body_html:
@flavioschuindt In your description, I do not see that if you ran this command to build the pip package:

bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/pip_package/build_pip_package /tmp

Without this, it is possible you have a stale pip package and not building the latest one.
body:
@flavioschuindt In your description, I do not see that if you ran this command to build the pip package:
```
bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/pip_package/build_pip_package /tmp
```
Without this, it is possible you have a stale pip package and not building the latest one.
